Authoritative Source of Thruth (ASoT), contains the Digital Viewpoint Model (DVM) that is organized in horizontal levels of abstraction
  • Computational Independent Model (CIM)
  • Platform Independent Model (PIM)
  • Platform Specific Model (PSM)
the vertical domains refer to the separation of concerns between:
  • Business
  • Information
  • Application
  • Infrastructure
the digital View Point Model is built so that specific stakeholders can access the part of the ASoT they are concern of in a form that they can easily consume.
